1375
01:13:37.030 --> 01:13:38.290
Bueno, lo hicimos los tres.

1376
01:13:44.170 --> 01:13:46.390
Yo atenderé.

1377
01:13:46.480 --> 01:13:48.830
Pase.

1378
01:13:49.870 --> 01:13:51.050
